<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<body>
    <section id="user-guide" style="padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <h2>User Guide</h2>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h3>1. How to Log Into the Website</h3>
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dai2jrbic/image/upload/v1748322916/Screenshot_848_wlwgrk.png" alt="How to log into website" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
        <p>Use your registered email and password to log into the website securely.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h3>2. How to Create a Listing</h3>
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dai2jrbic/image/upload/v1748322916/Screenshot_849_gigv10.png" alt="How to create a listing" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
        <p>Fill in the required details such as title, description, price, and upload images to create your own listing.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h3>3. How a Created Listing Looks Like & Modify It</h3>
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dai2jrbic/image/upload/v1748322916/Screenshot_852_pqmbkh.png" alt="Created listing and modifications" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
        <p>View your created listing, see details, and if needed, modify the listing details or delete it from your account dashboard.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="technologies" style="padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <h2>Technologies & Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
        <li><strong>Templating:</strong> EJS (Embedded JavaScript) templates used for dynamic UI rendering</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js with Express framework</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> MongoDB for storing listings, user data, and related content</li>
        <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Secure user authentication system for login, signup, and session management</li>
        <li><strong>Features:</strong> Create, view, modify, and delete listings; responsive UI; secure data handling</li>
    </ul>
</section>

</body>